        <h3>Source</h3>
                                    <div class="element-text">Grave marker photograph by Natasha Sheldon, "The Tophet of Carthage," <em>Archaeology</em>, May 8, 2008 at <a class="external" href="http://archaeology.suite101.com/article.cfm/tophet#ixzz0btZxUGMq">http://archaeology.suite101.com/article.cfm/tophet#ixzz0btZxUGMq</a>; Terracotta urn photograph by James Whitred of the Punic Project, American Schools of Oriental Research at <a class="external" href="http://www.mmdtkw.org/CNAf0227cCarthageTophet.jpg">http://www.mmdtkw.org/CNAf0227cCarthageTophet.jpg</a> (accessed January 6, 2010). Annotated by Susan Douglass and John Buescher.</div>
